description:
Always keen to look her best, Janet visits Dr Chris Moss for some 'freshening' and asks her new bestie Jackie along for support. Jackie and Ben host an extravagant Mexican themed housewarming party but when Ben confronts Gina about her issues with his wife, things go south of the border.
